des:
BNI Alliance Builders is a group of local business professionals who meet on a weekly basis to share knowledge, expand our network, facilitate referrals for our members, and not only believe in, but practice the philosophy of "Givers Gain". Our group is unique in that we only extend membership to one person per professional classification. We would like to invite you to experience a meeting for yourself.
